<div id="review_619553477" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/619553477" />
    <a title="Valerie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5893347-valerie"><img alt="Valerie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1440448903p2/5893347.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/619553477?book_show_action=true">Sep 01, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Valerie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Valerie" href="/user/show/5893347-valerie">Valerie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5893347-valerie?shelf=absolute-units">absolute-units</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5893347-valerie?shelf=nonfiction">nonfiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5893347-valerie?shelf=books-i-own">books-i-own</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5893347-valerie?shelf=history">history</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5893347-valerie?shelf=recommendations">recommendations</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5893347-valerie?shelf=5-star-tbr">5-star-tbr</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer619553477" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16148528567491671503">Three main thoughts: <br/>1) This book was incredible but I&apos;m fucking exhausted,<br/>2) I love my city so much,<br/>3) In the time it took me to read this book, 171,000 Americans died from covid-19. 20,000 of them were my neighbors. I don&apos;t know how to process this.</span>
  <span id="freeText16148528567491671503" style="display:none">Three main thoughts: <br />1) This book was incredible but I'm fucking exhausted,<br />2) I love my city so much,<br />3) In the time it took me to read this book, 171,000 Americans died from covid-19. 20,000 of them were my neighbors. I don't know how to process this.</span>
